Rating: 4
I veganized this recipe and was tremendously pleased. It seemed like more of a casserole than a bread when it went in the oven but came out great! Veganized: 4 yves breakfast patties, chopped and sauteed in apricot oil in place of sausage. firm tofu 1 cup, crumbled in place of eggs tofutti sour cream vegan gourmet chedder cheese, grated. Definitely making this again! I also used southwest corn ( a blend w/ black beans, and peppers) and canned diced chili peppers in place of fresh.

